description: The vice president of the student council and the younger sister of http://anidb.net/ch19202 [Tokugawa Yoshihiko], the student council president who supervises the "Buou Private Academy". Although she`s the daughter of the Tokugawa family because she`s a master with the naginata she often goes off to the battle. She also feels interested in http://anidb.net/ch19205 [Muneakira], her childhood friend, but she`s in the age where she can`t be honest with herself.
name: Tokugawa Sen
